snippet.title: CinemaSens
snippet.description:
No movie, tv series or music video is without hotness. Actually that is not true. There are lots of them without. Moving on... This channel exist mostly just to remind you of that hotness.

The components, elements, aspects and factors that go into deeming what is hot and what is not is an intricate routine of going with my gut feeling. Biology if you will. Also I will include hotness innuendo, hotness jokes, hot banter and other things referring to hotness. As a heterosexual male I will be focused on the sexual behavior in the human female as opposed to the human male.
 
I will try to upload a new tv series episode and/or music video and/or movie video during the week.
 
My channel is inspired by CinemaSins. As you can tell from the intro in my videos.
